WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
ظآزThat dayظآز

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
ظآزNothing stays together foreverظآز

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
ظآزI've quit romanceظآز

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
ظآزWho hasn't failed againظآز

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
ظآزCrying in deathظآز

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
ظآزAnd in lifeظآز

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
ظآزEven nowظآز

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
ظآزWe keep learningظآز

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
ظآزIt's no surpriseظآز

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
ظآزBeing happy is so hardظآز

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
ظآزWeirdly, I became a role modelظآز

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
ظآزOn the day we met again, we said hiظآز

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
ظآزIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintظآز

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
ظآزWho can do anything without regretظآز

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
ظآزI am all rightظآز

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
ظآزMay you live in peaceظآز

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
ظآزLet the world roarظآز

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
ظآزSounds like a carnivalظآز

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
ظآزBeing alive is never dullظآز

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
ظآزHow wonderful to be freeظآز

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
ظآزI became even better without youظآز

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
ظآزNothing can be perfectظآز

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
ظآزWe bless each other in painظآز

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
ظآزWe nod and smileظآز

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
ظآزMay we both be wellظآز

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:44.030
=Episode 22=

01:44.122 --> 01:45.002
Why don't you hit me?

01:45.002 --> 01:45.601
Hit me!

01:45.601 --> 01:46.002
Sorry!

01:46.002 --> 01:46.482
Hit me!

01:46.482 --> 01:47.202
It's all my fault.

01:47.441 --> 01:48.081
Go away!

01:48.241 --> 01:49.441
You! Let go of me!

01:49.441 --> 01:50.721
Why do you control me?

01:50.881 --> 01:51.601
Let go!

01:52.122 --> 01:53.042
Let go!

01:53.482 --> 01:54.361
Let go!

01:55.402 --> 01:56.762
Let go, you!

01:57.081 --> 01:57.682
Let go!

01:59.282 --> 02:00.081
Let go!

02:02.122 --> 02:04.161
Actually, I have one more merit.

02:04.441 --> 02:05.881
I'm a sincere person,

02:06.122 --> 02:07.682
especially to relationships.

02:08.041 --> 02:09.481
If one gives me a favor,

02:09.921 --> 02:11.122
I'll repay him tenfold.

02:11.242 --> 02:12.282
- Mr. Liang.
- I...

02:12.522 --> 02:13.641
You really have many merits.

02:14.601 --> 02:15.161
I'm home.

02:15.601 --> 02:16.242
Go to bed early.

02:16.282 --> 02:16.802
Thank you.

02:17.002 --> 02:17.641
Xu Yan.

02:18.641 --> 02:19.522
I really enjoy

02:19.522 --> 02:20.802
spending time alone with you.

02:21.522 --> 02:23.122
This feeling is unprecedented.

02:26.802 --> 02:29.641
Yuanhang has many projects,

02:30.682 --> 02:33.041
yet you still put effort in Yan Studio.

02:34.041 --> 02:35.321
I really appreciate it.

02:35.962 --> 02:37.402
So I want to find an opportunity

02:37.402 --> 02:38.562
to express my gratitude.

02:39.402 --> 02:40.362
Today,

02:40.362 --> 02:41.402
I can let you feel relaxed

02:41.441 --> 02:42.721
despite your busy schedule.

02:43.402 --> 02:44.362
It makes me happy too.

02:47.002 --> 02:48.161
In that case,

02:48.921 --> 02:50.082
we can only talk

02:50.082 --> 02:51.201
about work in the future?

02:51.441 --> 02:51.881
Exactly.

03:03.282 --> 03:04.201
Don't be alert.

03:04.842 --> 03:06.201
I'm truly single.

03:08.201 --> 03:09.481
But I'm still married.

03:14.962 --> 03:16.002
But I think

03:16.002 --> 03:17.962
there's a huge problem

03:18.242 --> 03:19.441
between you and Shen Haoming.

03:20.321 --> 03:21.362
You're aware of this too.

03:23.601 --> 03:24.641
Between him and me,

03:24.641 --> 03:26.282
there is indeed a problem to resolve.

03:26.321 --> 03:27.761
But that doesn't mean

03:27.761 --> 03:29.562
I can accept another man.

03:31.321 --> 03:31.842
Mr. Liang.

03:33.242 --> 03:34.441
Thank you

03:34.441 --> 03:36.522
for sharing
your cinematic world with me.

03:37.321 --> 03:38.402
I can tell

03:38.402 --> 03:41.481
you're someone really romantic,

03:43.282 --> 03:45.082
and never lonely.

03:48.041 --> 03:49.122
But in my mind,

03:49.282 --> 03:50.802
you're an excellent investor.

03:52.721 --> 03:53.881
I don't want

03:54.002 --> 03:55.881
any emotional entanglement

03:55.881 --> 03:57.481
to affect our current

03:57.481 --> 03:58.962
professional partnership.

03:59.282 --> 04:00.002
What do you think?

04:00.842 --> 04:01.562
I understand.

04:03.002 --> 04:04.962
If a woman rejects a man,

04:05.682 --> 04:07.402
it means the man
hasn't done well enough.

04:08.721 --> 04:09.601
I'll take your advice.

04:11.402 --> 04:12.881
I'll focus on being the investor.

04:14.242 --> 04:15.041
I believe

04:15.962 --> 04:18.562
the trust and mutual understanding
built in business

04:19.201 --> 04:20.722
will foster more genuine feelings.

04:21.362 --> 04:21.802
Alright.

04:22.162 --> 04:22.641
Bye then.

04:23.682 --> 04:24.201
Yan.

04:33.002 --> 04:34.122
Why do you come back alone?

04:34.722 --> 04:35.641
You should've told me,

04:36.081 --> 04:37.042
and I would pick you up.

04:38.521 --> 04:39.362
I brought her home.

04:43.242 --> 04:44.042
Thank you.

04:45.201 --> 04:46.521
After working hard,

04:46.682 --> 04:48.961
you still help me send my wife home.

04:49.321 --> 04:50.002
It's okay.

04:51.401 --> 04:52.881
Ms. Xu has moved out.

04:53.521 --> 04:55.722
Now you have to shuttle between places.

04:56.482 --> 04:57.521
She's that kind of person.

04:58.401 --> 04:59.881
Once she makes up her mind,

05:00.321 --> 05:02.081
she'll be devoted to it.

05:03.162 --> 05:03.841
It's late now.

05:04.441 --> 05:06.401
I won't invite you to my home then.

05:06.521 --> 05:06.961
No need.

05:07.441 --> 05:09.242
Ms. Xu and I will meet again tomorrow.

05:09.441 --> 05:11.281
You know, collaboration.

05:11.602 --> 05:12.441
We have to meet.

05:12.841 --> 05:13.362
I'm leaving.

05:13.362 --> 05:14.362
Looks like rain's coming.

05:14.521 --> 05:14.922
Bye.

05:15.081 --> 05:15.641
See you.

05:15.881 --> 05:16.682
Let me tell you.

05:17.722 --> 05:20.242
You're already a notorious playboy.

05:21.042 --> 05:23.321
Don't try to be a homewrecker now.

05:26.362 --> 05:26.841
Yan.

05:55.841 --> 05:56.641
What do you want?

05:57.401 --> 05:58.881
I'm quite happy today.

05:59.002 --> 05:59.922
Does that involve me?

06:07.802 --> 06:09.482
I heard you rejected Jiang Liang.

06:10.162 --> 06:10.881
You even told him

06:10.881 --> 06:12.521
our problem could be resolved.

06:13.002 --> 06:13.922
Of course.

06:14.641 --> 06:15.562
With a divorce.

06:26.162 --> 06:26.881
Shen Haoming.

06:29.201 --> 06:31.521
Our marriage started without dignity.

06:32.362 --> 06:33.841
Just take what we need.

06:35.081 --> 06:37.441
Now I just want us to part peacefully.

06:38.881 --> 06:39.881
Don't worry.

06:40.641 --> 06:41.881
I promised your parents

06:43.802 --> 06:45.401
to minimize public fallout.

06:46.081 --> 06:47.521
I'll keep my word.

06:48.881 --> 06:49.961
I just want us

06:50.401 --> 06:52.722
to smoothly obtain
the divorce certificate

06:52.722 --> 06:53.841
in our second attempt.

06:55.242 --> 06:56.081
Please cooperate.

07:05.201 --> 07:06.362
Remove your hand.

07:18.881 --> 07:20.162
Stop taking up the elevator.

07:41.362 --> 07:41.961
You're back.

07:42.362 --> 07:42.961
You're here.

07:43.722 --> 07:45.682
Got off work early
and help you clean up.

07:46.122 --> 07:47.122
I cut some fruits.

07:47.122 --> 07:47.841
Have some.

07:48.802 --> 07:49.321
Thanks.

07:51.242 --> 07:52.321
I saw from the balcony

07:52.321 --> 07:53.802
you returning with Jiang Liang.

07:54.002 --> 07:55.521
You're getting close lately.

07:56.281 --> 07:58.281
Not really, just for work.

07:59.802 --> 08:00.242
So,

08:00.482 --> 08:01.641
you feel nothing about him?

08:01.641 --> 08:02.281
Nothing.

08:22.242 --> 08:24.162
What about you and Shen Haoming?

08:26.602 --> 08:27.562
At the resort,

08:27.562 --> 08:28.761
something happened, right?

08:29.602 --> 08:31.281
You're quite nosy.

08:34.161 --> 08:35.561
You and Shen Haoming

08:35.561 --> 08:37.082
are finalizing the divorce,

08:37.561 --> 08:38.521
but I know

08:38.801 --> 08:41.401
you wanted to form a family with him.

08:42.842 --> 08:43.962
You loved him so much,

08:44.602 --> 08:45.921
and now you're parting.

08:46.082 --> 08:47.242
You must be sad.

08:47.281 --> 08:49.681
All my focus and energy now

08:50.122 --> 08:51.122
are on work.

08:51.401 --> 08:52.561
No time for others.

08:53.561 --> 08:55.082
It's good to focus on work,

08:55.482 --> 08:56.521
but I believe

08:56.801 --> 08:58.842
even decisive people get confused

08:58.921 --> 09:00.801
and don't know what to do sometimes.

09:01.921 --> 09:02.842
So I think

09:03.602 --> 09:05.041
you'd better think carefully

09:05.041 --> 09:06.561
and clarify your feelings

09:06.602 --> 09:07.521
before deciding.

09:07.602 --> 09:08.561
Strawberries are good.

09:08.561 --> 09:09.082
Try one.

09:09.242 --> 09:10.281
I know they're sweet.

09:10.761 --> 09:11.881
Am I right?

09:17.801 --> 09:19.082
You're quite right.

09:19.362 --> 09:20.202
You mentioned

09:20.202 --> 09:21.561
the peach blossom makeup concept.

09:22.002 --> 09:22.962
What about the plan?

09:23.641 --> 09:24.161
Moreover,

09:24.561 --> 09:25.482
want two assistants,

09:25.482 --> 09:26.002
right?

09:26.242 --> 09:27.122
How's that going?

09:27.322 --> 09:28.362
They are indeed sweet.

09:28.362 --> 09:28.842
I'm leaving.

09:28.842 --> 09:29.881
Check the resumes.

09:30.761 --> 09:32.401
What about your college exams?

09:32.521 --> 09:32.801
Right.

09:32.921 --> 09:34.002
Two subjects, right?

09:34.482 --> 09:35.761
Have you reviewed?

09:39.450 --> 09:42.000
ظآزI like it when it's just me and youظآز

09:46.330 --> 09:48.944
ظآزI think by now you know itظآز

09:50.416 --> 09:52.578
ظآزAbout you and meظآز

09:53.114 --> 09:55.717
ظآزThere's not a thing that I wouldn't doظآز

10:00.026 --> 10:02.870
ظآزRight now just to be here with youظآز

10:07.290 --> 10:08.432
ظآزI like youظآز

10:08.432 --> 10:10.672
ظآزHere in my armsظآز

10:14.138 --> 10:15.184
ظآزI like youظآز

10:15.184 --> 10:17.712
ظآزHere in my armsظآز

10:21.498 --> 10:23.152
ظآزWhat already happenedظآز

10:23.376 --> 10:24.624
ظآزFeeling so lost and feelingظآز

10:24.624 --> 10:26.618
ظآزSo much distractionsظآز

10:26.810 --> 10:27.888
ظآزNever imaginedظآز

10:27.888 --> 10:29.990
ظآزYou'd stay by my sideظآز

10:31.322 --> 10:33.264
ظآزComforting my sorrowsظآز

10:35.194 --> 10:36.951
ظآزOn the midnight streetsظآز

10:37.146 --> 10:38.384
ظآزIn shadowed cornersظآز

10:38.761 --> 10:42.161
(My love for you has been genuine.)

10:43.842 --> 10:45.122
I truly love you.

10:48.432 --> 10:50.384
ظآزAt that moment, the worldظآز

10:50.384 --> 10:53.744
ظآزJust you and meظآز

10:55.248 --> 10:57.183
ظآزEnjoying the city lifeظآز

10:57.183 --> 11:01.264
ظآزHolding your handظآز

11:02.544 --> 11:08.848
ظآزAnd I just want to tell youظآز

11:08.848 --> 11:11.583
ظآزAs if in the movieظآز

11:12.208 --> 11:15.440
ظآزForever in my heartظآز

11:15.440 --> 11:22.320
ظآزI like it when it's just me and youظآز

11:22.320 --> 11:24.844
ظآزI think by now you know itظآز

11:26.320 --> 11:29.082
ظآزDo you know, my dearظآز

11:29.082 --> 11:30.002
Throughout this trip,

11:30.602 --> 11:32.041
I've carried this ring with me,

11:35.002 --> 11:36.442
hoping you can forgive me.

11:38.561 --> 11:40.202
Give me one chance, okay?

11:40.202 --> 11:42.192
ظآزAbout me and youظآز

12:09.881 --> 12:10.561
Stop drinking.

12:11.602 --> 12:12.202
Give it to me.

12:30.801 --> 12:31.801
Why are you still here?

12:32.761 --> 12:33.801
Get out now!

12:35.921 --> 12:37.761
Look at what you have become.

12:38.281 --> 12:39.602
Learn to love yourself

12:39.602 --> 12:40.561
before loving others.

12:41.881 --> 12:43.362
Be an independent woman

12:43.442 --> 12:44.681
who stays clear-headed.

12:45.362 --> 12:46.281
Have your own career,

12:46.322 --> 12:47.281
your own life,

12:48.202 --> 12:49.641
and courage to walk away anytime.

12:50.962 --> 12:52.801
Be a relaxed and independent woman.

12:53.041 --> 12:54.161
Live for yourself.

12:57.161 --> 12:58.962
If I can't be with Haoming,

13:01.761 --> 13:03.921
I'd rather stay single forever.

13:07.041 --> 13:08.401
Stay single forever?

13:09.281 --> 13:10.962
I thought about this before.

13:12.401 --> 13:13.122
Let me show you.

13:15.442 --> 13:16.322
When we get old,

13:16.962 --> 13:19.281
we could find a premium nursing home.

13:21.002 --> 13:21.482
And then,

13:21.561 --> 13:24.161
we could take art and music classes.

13:24.761 --> 13:25.681
When we get bored,

13:25.962 --> 13:27.401
go sing karaoke, or dance.

13:27.641 --> 13:28.202
Interesting?

13:29.482 --> 13:30.442
Here, look.

13:32.202 --> 13:33.521
This one is run by my friend.

13:33.842 --> 13:34.681
Go visit sometime?

13:42.082 --> 13:43.202
Are you insane?

13:43.842 --> 13:45.561
Who would be in a nursing home with you?

13:48.082 --> 13:48.561
Let go!

13:48.761 --> 13:49.482
Let go of me!

14:16.801 --> 14:17.521
Thinking?

14:18.761 --> 14:19.681
All these years,

14:20.401 --> 14:22.082
you've been chasing Shen Haoming,

14:22.602 --> 14:24.161
yet he married someone else,

14:24.881 --> 14:26.322
didn't even care about you.

14:28.161 --> 14:29.761
If there's a chance to ruin him,

14:31.242 --> 14:32.242
are you interested?

14:37.161 --> 14:39.002
Why suggest that?

14:47.082 --> 14:47.842
Because of you.

14:49.442 --> 14:50.161
I don't want

14:52.202 --> 14:54.122
you sinking deeper into darkness.

15:06.722 --> 15:07.322
Chen Lin.

15:08.521 --> 15:09.962
Still haven't eaten at this hour?

15:10.842 --> 15:12.122
Mr. Shen is out.

15:12.242 --> 15:14.082
He told me to put this in his office.

15:15.681 --> 15:16.242
I'm going.

15:16.242 --> 15:17.041
Want my help?

15:18.722 --> 15:19.442
Well,

15:19.962 --> 15:20.602
thanks then.

15:21.362 --> 15:22.202
No need.

15:22.401 --> 15:23.041
Go eat now.

15:40.666 --> 15:42.864
(Proposal for Strategic Cooperation
with Moscow Arbat Commercial Center)

15:47.290 --> 15:49.296
(Proposal for Strategic Cooperation
with Moscow Arbat Commercial Center)

15:56.890 --> 15:59.696
(Yan Studio)

16:00.281 --> 16:01.242
As you can see,

16:01.281 --> 16:02.641
our first batch of videos

16:03.442 --> 16:04.602
exceeds 10,000 views each.

16:05.122 --> 16:06.281
The top video

16:06.281 --> 16:07.681
even surpasses 60,000 clicks.

16:08.161 --> 16:09.881
Therefore, I think we can move on

16:09.881 --> 16:11.161
to production phase.

16:11.602 --> 16:12.362
Fantastic!

16:12.362 --> 16:14.122
Finally reaching phase two.

16:15.362 --> 16:15.881
Okay.

16:16.202 --> 16:17.962
Today's meeting is

16:17.962 --> 16:19.281
to finalize first collection

16:19.322 --> 16:20.602
and production quantities.

16:23.521 --> 16:26.041
I've compiled all sample video metrics

16:26.041 --> 16:27.041
for review.

16:27.122 --> 16:28.881
These five pieces
received the most likes

16:28.881 --> 16:30.242
and the highest engagement.

16:30.681 --> 16:32.401
And the highest number
of positive reviews.

16:33.002 --> 16:33.641
In my opinion,

16:33.641 --> 16:35.362
sometimes we have to trust the netizens.

16:35.842 --> 16:37.362
Their taste is as good as mine.

16:37.842 --> 16:39.281
I also think they are the best.

16:40.161 --> 16:42.281
Let me share a different perspective.

16:42.921 --> 16:44.842
The biggest highlight
of these five pieces

16:44.881 --> 16:46.962
is that they all use brocade fabric.

16:47.401 --> 16:50.002
But this also is
their biggest challenge.

16:50.041 --> 16:51.281
Because this brocade fabric

16:51.281 --> 16:54.161
is handwoven by ethnic minorities.

16:54.362 --> 16:55.761
So, it showcases

16:55.761 --> 16:58.082
such intricate craftsmanship
and exquisite texture.

16:58.921 --> 17:02.641
However, their output
is extremely limited.

17:03.482 --> 17:04.162
Well,

17:04.321 --> 17:06.041
should we first set up a cooperation

17:06.041 --> 17:07.442
with the producers?

17:08.841 --> 17:10.642
But hand-weaving is always

17:10.682 --> 17:12.361
slower compared to machinery.

17:13.041 --> 17:14.922
What if they can't meet our demand?

17:15.722 --> 17:18.081
I've thought about this before.

17:18.882 --> 17:21.402
But we're still in the early phase,

17:22.202 --> 17:24.561
so a small-batch
yet high-quality approach

17:24.561 --> 17:25.561
suits us better.

17:25.841 --> 17:26.442
Financially,

17:26.442 --> 17:28.002
it's safer and more secure.

17:29.202 --> 17:30.041
For the first batch,

17:30.041 --> 17:31.536
I want us to focus on

17:31.696 --> 17:32.601
excellence,

17:32.761 --> 17:33.361
precision,

17:33.841 --> 17:34.642
and reputation.

17:35.561 --> 17:37.281
As for what Yao mentioned,

17:38.202 --> 17:39.321
we can transform

17:39.482 --> 17:40.962
the challenge of brocade production

17:41.281 --> 17:44.841
into online marketing
advantages and highlights.

17:45.882 --> 17:47.002
Many niche designer brands

17:47.002 --> 17:48.321
are now adopting

17:48.561 --> 17:49.722
a limited edition

17:49.722 --> 17:50.841
plus pre-sale model.

17:50.922 --> 17:52.281
We can consider this approach too.

17:53.722 --> 17:56.442
For the five styles for the first batch,
100 pieces each.

17:56.601 --> 17:58.081
If we can achieve this,

17:58.642 --> 18:00.081
it could be a success.

18:04.841 --> 18:05.402
Xiaowan,

18:05.962 --> 18:07.482
any ideas for online promotion?

18:08.202 --> 18:10.761
We could organize
reward-based activities

18:10.801 --> 18:11.722
to extend the timeline.

18:11.761 --> 18:14.121
This would buy us time for production.

18:16.242 --> 18:18.002
Any other problem to discuss?

18:19.121 --> 18:20.041
Based on Wan's plan,

18:20.041 --> 18:21.922
I'll recruit more influencers

18:21.962 --> 18:23.242
to promote us.

18:23.521 --> 18:25.081
Regarding the fees

18:25.242 --> 18:26.801
for these influencers,

18:26.801 --> 18:28.081
could you give me an estimate?

18:28.242 --> 18:28.521
Sure.

18:28.561 --> 18:29.361
I'll send it to you.

18:29.521 --> 18:30.002
Good.

18:32.722 --> 18:34.841
I can reach out to bloggers,

18:34.841 --> 18:36.121
offer them free makeup services,

18:36.121 --> 18:37.962
and let them wear our outfits in posts.

18:37.962 --> 18:39.162
That should help, right?

18:46.121 --> 18:47.202
Why did you ask to meet?

18:47.722 --> 18:48.962
Can't I just want to see you?

18:49.202 --> 18:50.561
Join me for afternoon tea?

18:51.002 --> 18:51.922
Sure.

18:54.041 --> 18:54.801
How have you been?

18:55.442 --> 18:56.642
Haven't seen you in days.

18:57.162 --> 18:58.442
Focus on work

18:58.442 --> 19:00.442
or on someone?

19:03.882 --> 19:05.841
No one understands me like you do.

19:06.321 --> 19:07.402
Same old me.

19:08.321 --> 19:11.242
I can't stand seeing
female friends suffering,

19:11.242 --> 19:12.561
so I have to help them.

19:12.761 --> 19:13.682
What can I do?

19:14.402 --> 19:17.521
There are too many female friends
you want to help.

19:18.281 --> 19:19.482
Which one this time?

19:21.482 --> 19:21.962
Xu Yan.

19:24.722 --> 19:25.601
Xu Yan?

19:29.642 --> 19:30.801
Are you out of your mind?

19:32.041 --> 19:33.962
Xu Yan is Shen Haoming's wife.

19:34.361 --> 19:35.521
We're in the negotiation.

19:37.002 --> 19:38.002
So what?

19:38.321 --> 19:39.521
I'm her investor.

19:39.962 --> 19:40.561
Besides,

19:40.561 --> 19:41.482
heard the rumors?

19:41.482 --> 19:42.521
They're getting divorced.

19:42.601 --> 19:43.801
I don't care about rumors.

19:44.442 --> 19:46.442
But I don't want you to help her.

19:56.242 --> 19:56.962
Haochen.

19:58.321 --> 19:59.402
What is it, Coach Lu?

19:59.682 --> 20:00.722
I want to recommend you

20:00.761 --> 20:02.922
for this year's
Junior Equestrian Championship.

20:03.521 --> 20:04.121
However,

20:04.121 --> 20:05.841
we need to consult
your family's opinions.

20:06.041 --> 20:07.281
Have your family come over

20:08.162 --> 20:10.682
to discuss your training schedule
for the second half.

20:11.761 --> 20:13.361
Just call my sister-in-law.

20:13.442 --> 20:14.922
She handles all my affairs.

20:15.281 --> 20:15.682
Alright.

20:15.882 --> 20:16.841
I'll contact her.

20:21.482 --> 20:22.002
Haoming.

20:22.202 --> 20:23.041
Come here.

20:23.081 --> 20:24.761
I've got amazing news!

20:25.041 --> 20:26.642
If you want to join the championship,

20:26.642 --> 20:29.361
the technical difficulty and
training intensity will both increase.

20:29.361 --> 20:30.922
Haochen is very interested himself.

20:31.162 --> 20:33.321
I wonder what you two think.

20:36.521 --> 20:37.922
Haochen has trained for four years.

20:38.601 --> 20:39.841
If he's interested,

20:40.081 --> 20:41.321
I'll definitely support him.

20:45.801 --> 20:47.202
Honey, what do you think?

20:54.801 --> 20:55.482
Coach Lu,

20:56.402 --> 20:57.761
Haochen's records show

20:57.761 --> 20:59.521
he's completed
over 350 training sessions.

21:02.281 --> 21:03.722
If he wants to participate,

21:03.722 --> 21:04.962
we'll definitely support him.

21:06.682 --> 21:07.841
But I have one question.

21:08.242 --> 21:09.561
He's nearly 160 cm tall.

21:10.482 --> 21:12.242
His current horse might be too small.

21:12.841 --> 21:14.002
If it's too small,

21:14.162 --> 21:15.801
jumping obstacles could be dangerous.

21:18.281 --> 21:18.722
Yes.

21:18.882 --> 21:19.682
For the competition,

21:19.682 --> 21:21.801
we'll adjust equipment to his height.

21:22.361 --> 21:23.242
Glad to hear that.

21:23.321 --> 21:23.642
Okay.

21:24.242 --> 21:26.482
I'll start working on the registration.

21:27.321 --> 21:27.882
Thank you.

21:28.682 --> 21:29.242
- Thanks.
- Not at all.

21:29.242 --> 21:29.801
Thank you.

21:36.242 --> 21:37.081
Call me anytime.

21:37.242 --> 21:37.761
I'm leaving.

21:39.121 --> 21:40.002
Wait!

21:42.682 --> 21:43.361
Well,

21:44.041 --> 21:45.922
the fresh juices here are tasty.

21:45.922 --> 21:46.841
Want to try some?

21:48.402 --> 21:48.801
Sure!

21:48.801 --> 21:49.801
I'll go get you some.

21:50.081 --> 21:51.002
Wait for me!

21:59.561 --> 22:00.922
The juice here is pretty good.

22:03.442 --> 22:04.162
I know.

22:19.722 --> 22:20.561
Sit down and wait?

22:30.361 --> 22:32.162
Please tell Haochen

22:32.841 --> 22:34.002
I need to leave now.

22:34.801 --> 22:36.561
I left a meeting halfway to come here.

22:37.682 --> 22:38.081
Okay.

22:38.761 --> 22:39.361
Thanks.

22:56.601 --> 22:57.202
Where's she?

22:57.841 --> 22:59.002
She had work to attend to

22:59.801 --> 23:00.281
and left.

23:00.682 --> 23:02.482
Why are you still sitting here?

23:03.242 --> 23:04.041
Oh my!

23:06.162 --> 23:08.202
You're driving me crazy!

23:08.442 --> 23:10.281
Even I know

23:10.361 --> 23:11.722
you should fix your mistakes.

23:11.962 --> 23:13.841
You made her mad,

23:13.922 --> 23:15.002
and now she's ignoring you.

23:15.002 --> 23:16.402
You need to do something!

23:19.642 --> 23:21.081
Yan has been sincere

23:21.722 --> 23:23.041
to Haochen.

23:24.402 --> 23:25.281
After all,

23:25.962 --> 23:27.361
it's all for you.

23:28.601 --> 23:30.081
Otherwise, to her,

23:30.442 --> 23:32.281
Haochen is just some random child.

23:35.561 --> 23:37.121
She's always adored Haochen.

23:37.922 --> 23:38.922
Why involves me?

23:39.361 --> 23:40.482
Of course, it involves you.

23:40.761 --> 23:42.002
"Love me, love my dog."

23:42.722 --> 23:44.561
She loves you,

23:45.002 --> 23:47.121
so she values our family.

23:48.202 --> 23:49.642
After you two married,

23:50.121 --> 23:51.081
she's treated me,

23:51.561 --> 23:52.321
your father,

23:52.402 --> 23:53.121
and Haochen

23:53.402 --> 23:54.642
with sincerity.

23:55.081 --> 23:57.601
Her care has always been tangible.

23:58.281 --> 23:59.841
And I truly felt it.

24:02.761 --> 24:05.321
After decades in business,

24:06.121 --> 24:08.601
I've encountered all types of people.

24:09.962 --> 24:11.442
But when Yan looks at you,

24:12.081 --> 24:15.321
I can tell how deeply she loves you.

24:18.442 --> 24:19.801
Actually,

24:19.962 --> 24:21.402
it's part of my fault that you two

24:22.041 --> 24:23.442
are getting divorce now.

24:25.841 --> 24:26.922
From the start,

24:27.202 --> 24:29.521
I wanted you to marry someone matched

24:30.402 --> 24:32.601
so I was harsh to Yan,

24:33.402 --> 24:34.642
and tried every mean

24:34.761 --> 24:35.801
to drive her away.

24:37.321 --> 24:39.002
I deeply regret that now.

24:41.002 --> 24:42.801
Had I not done those,

24:43.482 --> 24:45.642
she wouldn't have lied
about her family backgrounds

24:46.482 --> 24:48.242
to prove herself.

24:51.041 --> 24:52.722
I've no right

24:53.121 --> 24:54.361
to blame her for deceiving me.

24:56.162 --> 24:57.081
From the beginning,

24:58.162 --> 24:59.041
I'd already decided

24:59.882 --> 25:01.801
to hide Haochen's background.

25:04.801 --> 25:07.041
Now that you've talked things through,

25:07.482 --> 25:09.922
I think you may get back together.

25:12.202 --> 25:12.801
Haoming.

25:14.321 --> 25:15.242
I truly cherish Yan

25:15.242 --> 25:16.242
as my daughter-in-law.

25:18.041 --> 25:21.482
She reminds me of my younger self.

25:22.882 --> 25:23.882
Driven,

25:24.561 --> 25:26.121
hardworking,

25:27.162 --> 25:28.321
able to handle both society

25:29.041 --> 25:30.081
and hard labor.

25:31.041 --> 25:33.041
When she did supermarket live streams,

25:33.841 --> 25:34.761
she swallowed her pride

25:35.041 --> 25:36.002
and standing on her own.

25:36.761 --> 25:38.321
She made no excuses

25:38.321 --> 25:39.882
for her mistakes,

25:40.601 --> 25:42.041
but fight for what she wanted

25:42.321 --> 25:44.162
through sheer determination.

25:45.922 --> 25:47.242
That's when I knew

25:48.002 --> 25:50.561
she was meant to be
the hostess of Shen Family.

25:51.321 --> 25:52.121
Just like you,

25:54.761 --> 25:56.761
she's a pillar of our family.

25:57.482 --> 25:58.321
Promise me.

25:59.081 --> 26:00.642
No matter what it takes,

26:01.482 --> 26:03.081
bring Yan back.

26:05.081 --> 26:06.242
When I married her,

26:07.761 --> 26:09.361
I vowed to never let go.

26:12.722 --> 26:13.561
You can do this.

26:30.402 --> 26:30.801
Come on.

26:30.801 --> 26:31.561
Good job.

26:32.041 --> 26:32.922
That's it for today.

26:35.281 --> 26:35.801
Lin.

26:35.922 --> 26:37.041
I'll book you again.

26:37.402 --> 26:37.922
Thank you.

26:39.041 --> 26:39.801
See you Friday.

26:39.841 --> 26:40.121
Got it.

26:40.321 --> 26:40.841
Bye.

26:41.402 --> 26:41.922
Take care.

26:47.922 --> 26:48.442
Zheng!

26:49.121 --> 26:50.121
Are you okay?

26:50.402 --> 26:51.120
Twisted my ankle.

26:51.321 --> 26:52.162
Can you move?

26:52.442 --> 26:52.922
It hurts.

26:53.121 --> 26:53.761
I can't move.

26:55.002 --> 26:56.002
Let's go to the hospital.

26:56.561 --> 26:57.281
Don't delay.

26:57.601 --> 26:58.041
Let's go.

26:58.041 --> 26:58.601
Come on.

26:58.882 --> 26:59.482
Hello, sir.

27:02.722 --> 27:04.801
The doctor let him stay
a few days for observation.

27:11.601 --> 27:12.162
Bye.

27:27.002 --> 27:27.761
Scumbag!

27:28.482 --> 27:30.402
I knew you weren't sincere with Lin.

27:32.002 --> 27:32.601
Lin.

27:33.041 --> 27:34.642
Come to the hospital cafeteria now.

27:34.882 --> 27:36.281
See what Yu Yiming's been doing

27:36.281 --> 27:37.242
(Jingzhou Yuekang Hospital, Outpatient)
behind your back.

27:45.642 --> 27:46.722
Outrageous.

27:47.121 --> 27:48.442
Just now she held his hand.

27:48.841 --> 27:50.521
Now he's patting her shoulder.

27:50.922 --> 27:51.882
They've been together

27:51.882 --> 27:52.962
for 26 minutes.

27:53.202 --> 27:54.121
In front of me,

27:54.121 --> 27:55.682
he keeps declaring his love for you.

27:56.002 --> 27:56.962
Look what he's doing!

27:57.402 --> 27:59.162
Touchy-feely in public.

27:59.162 --> 28:00.081
No sense of propriety.

28:00.962 --> 28:02.962
He's practically a male coquette!

28:03.482 --> 28:04.242
Shut up!

28:05.121 --> 28:06.162
Stop rambling.

28:07.841 --> 28:09.202
Move away.

28:12.202 --> 28:12.761
Lin.

28:13.202 --> 28:13.722
Lin.

28:14.882 --> 28:15.521
Scumbag!

28:15.601 --> 28:16.361
Senior.

28:18.882 --> 28:20.848
This is my first patient

28:23.600 --> 28:25.761
who died since I became a resident.

28:32.242 --> 28:32.922
Wenjin.

28:34.801 --> 28:36.642
I've been through these too.

28:39.081 --> 28:40.642
There are patients we want to save

28:41.962 --> 28:42.761
but can't.

28:43.242 --> 28:45.761
When we face their grieving family,
we don't know what to say.

28:46.761 --> 28:47.882
I know

28:49.002 --> 28:50.242
how hard it is

28:52.121 --> 28:53.482
for you.

28:54.601 --> 28:55.761
But as doctors,

28:56.081 --> 28:58.242
we must face this and overcome it.

29:01.321 --> 29:03.202
There are other patients waiting for us.

29:03.561 --> 29:04.041
Lin.

29:05.521 --> 29:06.081
Lin.

29:08.002 --> 29:08.521
Lin!

29:10.482 --> 29:11.601
Please listen to me.

29:11.962 --> 29:12.402
Go ahead.

29:13.561 --> 29:15.121
I know you're hurting.

29:16.442 --> 29:19.761
But you must see his true nature.

29:21.121 --> 29:23.002
Yu Yiming's conditions are good.

29:24.242 --> 29:24.801
I admit that.

29:26.682 --> 29:28.482
But people living in big cities

29:28.682 --> 29:30.321
think realistically.

29:31.281 --> 29:32.601
Your social status, background,

29:32.601 --> 29:33.321
education, and job

29:33.321 --> 29:34.521
are worlds apart from his.

29:34.722 --> 29:36.402
Do you really think he doesn't care?

29:39.162 --> 29:39.482
Lin Tao.

29:39.482 --> 29:40.841
I don't care what you saw.

29:40.962 --> 29:41.841
I just believe

29:41.841 --> 29:43.761
that Yu Yiming is not that kind of man.

29:44.442 --> 29:45.002
Well, Lin.

29:45.002 --> 29:46.761
Why don't you believe me?

29:46.761 --> 29:48.121
I'm the one who truly...

29:53.722 --> 29:54.962
Where's that bruise from?

29:55.442 --> 29:56.521
You fought?

29:56.922 --> 29:57.521
Well...

29:58.402 --> 30:00.080
I'm now a sparring partner
at an MMA gym.

30:01.761 --> 30:02.482
Why?

30:03.202 --> 30:03.962
To take punches.

30:04.642 --> 30:05.801
You like hitting people.

30:06.002 --> 30:06.841
No problem.

30:07.202 --> 30:08.482
If hitting me makes you happy,

30:08.922 --> 30:09.962
just do it.

30:10.162 --> 30:10.682
Lin.

30:11.081 --> 30:13.442
I'm ready to be
your punching bag for life.

30:19.561 --> 30:20.202
Lin Tao.

30:21.081 --> 30:22.202
The matter between us

30:22.761 --> 30:24.041
has dragged on long enough.

30:27.162 --> 30:29.081
Can we calmly

30:29.081 --> 30:30.321
talk it through today?

30:32.242 --> 30:32.801
Okay.

30:36.121 --> 30:36.682
I know

30:37.962 --> 30:39.242
you gave a lot

30:40.002 --> 30:41.041
to this relationship.

30:42.002 --> 30:43.722
But we've both realized we're not right

30:43.722 --> 30:44.882
for each other.

30:45.402 --> 30:47.041
Breaking up is the best choice.

30:49.121 --> 30:50.962
We're never getting back together.

30:53.561 --> 30:54.442
So,

30:55.402 --> 30:56.722
I hope you can let go.

30:58.442 --> 30:59.801
Don't you want me to be happy?

31:01.682 --> 31:03.722
I am now.

31:04.601 --> 31:05.601
Look,

31:05.601 --> 31:06.521
I've got my sister

31:06.922 --> 31:09.041
and my startup team by my side.

31:09.601 --> 31:11.642
My life is full and busy.

31:14.121 --> 31:15.041
I also hope

31:16.642 --> 31:18.402
that you get back

31:18.601 --> 31:19.922
on your own path.

31:20.761 --> 31:21.321
Lin Tao.

31:23.361 --> 31:24.482
I wish you well too.

31:30.162 --> 31:30.642
I'll leave.

31:42.202 --> 31:42.922
Lin.

31:44.402 --> 31:45.552
Take good care of yourself.

31:48.962 --> 31:49.922
How's Xu Yan's company

31:49.922 --> 31:51.041
doing lately?

31:51.402 --> 31:53.561
They're doing great.

31:53.962 --> 31:55.521
Their newly released short videos

31:55.601 --> 31:56.841
get over 10,000 likes,

31:57.482 --> 32:00.281
all with much better quality.

32:01.682 --> 32:02.521
Currently,

32:02.682 --> 32:03.761
this market is competitive.

32:04.002 --> 32:05.521
With numerous production stages,

32:06.002 --> 32:07.722
achieving such results this fast

32:08.002 --> 32:08.841
is truly remarkable.

32:10.722 --> 32:13.482
No wonder Jiang Liang
has been showing off.

32:14.281 --> 32:15.841
Actually, I think

32:16.402 --> 32:17.922
Yan works hard

32:18.442 --> 32:19.482
just to prove her worth

32:19.482 --> 32:20.561
and strength to you.

32:21.041 --> 32:22.002
These days

32:22.281 --> 32:25.002
people want equal and balanced love.

32:25.321 --> 32:26.841
She's an independent woman.

32:27.682 --> 32:29.002
Surely she wants to succeed first

32:29.002 --> 32:29.801
before returning.

32:31.722 --> 32:32.682
Really?

32:32.922 --> 32:33.482
Absolutely.

32:33.808 --> 32:34.642
Think about it.

32:34.962 --> 32:37.801
If she really wanted to cut ties,

32:38.321 --> 32:40.041
why would she agree to the resort trip?

32:40.442 --> 32:41.841
Why would she help you

32:42.202 --> 32:43.482
win over Mr. Baraikin?

32:46.642 --> 32:47.242
Three days.

32:47.521 --> 32:48.521
You have to be together

32:48.521 --> 32:50.002
all the time,

32:50.482 --> 32:51.722
pretending to be close,

32:52.521 --> 32:53.882
even sharing a room.

32:55.801 --> 32:56.642
Let me tell you.

32:57.402 --> 32:59.801
If a woman truly hates a man,

33:00.081 --> 33:01.761
she wouldn't spend
even a second with him.

33:03.882 --> 33:04.882
Remember

33:05.242 --> 33:08.281
the romantic room at Yanbo Resort?

33:08.722 --> 33:09.882
That passionate setup.

33:11.002 --> 33:12.321
Yan didn't object at all, right?

33:15.761 --> 33:18.321
You did a good job.

33:18.561 --> 33:21.722
If she truly had no feelings left,
why would she do that?

33:22.601 --> 33:24.482
But she keeps wanting a divorce.

33:25.162 --> 33:26.521
That's just anger talking.

33:28.321 --> 33:30.202
My girlfriend used to threaten breakup

33:30.521 --> 33:31.402
when got mad.

33:31.682 --> 33:32.242
Really.

33:34.962 --> 33:37.162
How did you become such a smooth talker?

33:37.962 --> 33:38.482
Sit down.

33:40.601 --> 33:41.162
Keep going.

33:44.402 --> 33:45.561
Now,

33:45.841 --> 33:47.682
to win her back

33:47.722 --> 33:48.801
by direct communication

33:49.281 --> 33:50.361
is hard.

33:50.841 --> 33:53.081
But there's a method that always works.

33:53.162 --> 33:53.922
What is it?

33:54.722 --> 33:55.601
Indirect strategy.

33:56.402 --> 33:57.841
Go find her friends.

33:57.962 --> 33:58.801
That would help.

33:58.922 --> 33:59.402
No use.

33:59.761 --> 34:01.482
I tried Qiao Lin, but she refused.

34:02.041 --> 34:03.361
What about male friends?

34:04.002 --> 34:04.922
At such times,

34:05.081 --> 34:06.482
men often understand each other.

34:08.561 --> 34:10.442
Male friends?

34:13.762 --> 34:14.882
She does have one.

34:42.041 --> 34:42.704
Coming!

34:44.592 --> 34:45.872
Qiao Lin. Perfect timing.

34:45.872 --> 34:47.792
I'm making breakfast
and want to bring you some.

34:47.792 --> 34:48.521
Take any seat.

34:54.561 --> 34:55.762
- I'll get you some fruit.
- Wait.

34:56.362 --> 34:57.641
I have something to say.

34:58.842 --> 34:59.561
Go ahead.

35:00.641 --> 35:01.521
Sit down.

35:08.561 --> 35:09.201
Yu Yiming.

35:13.161 --> 35:13.882
I like you.

35:17.002 --> 35:18.442
- Qiao Lin, actually...
- Let me finish.

35:18.561 --> 35:19.161
Okay.

35:24.081 --> 35:27.601
Yes, I always do what I want,

35:28.161 --> 35:29.962
but I'm not that naive.

35:32.121 --> 35:33.282
I'm very aware

35:33.442 --> 35:35.521
of the real differences between us.

35:36.041 --> 35:38.201
Those can't be ignored.

35:42.402 --> 35:43.842
I know there are

35:44.282 --> 35:45.681
many outstanding people around you.

35:45.962 --> 35:47.802
Like that female doctor

35:47.802 --> 35:49.081
I saw in the cafeteria.

35:49.762 --> 35:51.081
Realistically,

35:51.201 --> 35:52.681
they're more successful,

35:52.721 --> 35:55.362
and also better matches for you.

35:55.482 --> 35:57.362
You share the same profession

35:58.161 --> 35:59.521
so you'd have more topics

35:59.601 --> 36:00.561
and pursuits in common.

36:01.081 --> 36:01.442
However,

36:02.762 --> 36:05.121
I don't think this means

36:05.121 --> 36:06.322
I'm unworthy of liking you.

36:10.482 --> 36:12.041
I believe

36:12.521 --> 36:13.962
you have the right to choose.

36:15.002 --> 36:15.612
So...

36:16.400 --> 36:18.362
If you think

36:18.362 --> 36:20.282
she is more suitable,

36:22.802 --> 36:25.241
I won't force it.

36:32.842 --> 36:33.482
Qiao Lin.

36:37.121 --> 36:38.201
What's with you today?

36:39.561 --> 36:40.762
Did something happen to you?

36:44.721 --> 36:45.882
Yesterday,

36:45.882 --> 36:47.041
at the hospital cafeteria,

36:47.041 --> 36:48.521
I saw you with Dr. Xu.

36:49.402 --> 36:50.402
She looked distressed

36:50.681 --> 36:52.121
and you tried to comfort her.

36:52.201 --> 36:53.362
She seemed to need you.

36:56.282 --> 36:57.721
I-I don't know what to say.

36:59.442 --> 37:00.208
Didn't sleep well?

37:04.161 --> 37:05.442
Yesterday,

37:06.081 --> 37:06.922
it was her first time

37:07.002 --> 37:08.241
losing a patient.

37:08.362 --> 37:09.521
So I consoled her.

37:10.041 --> 37:10.922
But rest assured.

37:11.241 --> 37:13.121
There's nothing beyond colleagues.

37:13.561 --> 37:14.041
Really.

37:16.762 --> 37:17.802
I trust you.

37:18.962 --> 37:20.282
Also, I trust your character.

37:20.721 --> 37:23.482
But the reality between us

37:24.282 --> 37:25.521
still exist.

37:26.882 --> 37:27.962
I don't know

37:27.962 --> 37:30.081
if it will create obstacles

37:30.201 --> 37:31.241
for us.

37:32.402 --> 37:33.161
So...

37:34.482 --> 37:37.721
Maybe we should

37:38.161 --> 37:39.362
take a week apart

37:39.442 --> 37:40.521
to think it over.

37:42.402 --> 37:43.482
No, Qiao Lin. I don't...

37:45.521 --> 37:46.362
This week,

37:47.081 --> 37:48.002
don't contact me.

37:55.842 --> 37:56.362
Okay.

37:58.482 --> 37:59.762
Once I confirm it,

37:59.762 --> 38:00.681
I'll message you.

38:06.922 --> 38:07.402
Alright.

38:09.842 --> 38:10.482
How's it going?

38:11.041 --> 38:12.322
I've secured cooperation

38:12.322 --> 38:14.842
with three weaving villages
for brocade production.

38:15.442 --> 38:17.282
They'll supply us long-term.

38:18.442 --> 38:19.362
That's good.

38:19.721 --> 38:20.882
Now we can send orders

38:20.882 --> 38:21.762
to the factory.

38:21.962 --> 38:22.601
I'll follow up.

38:22.601 --> 38:23.241
Wait a second.

38:24.442 --> 38:25.002
Sit down.

38:28.962 --> 38:30.681
Did something happen?

38:31.241 --> 38:31.962
Look at you.

38:39.802 --> 38:41.282
There are only two people

38:41.322 --> 38:42.442
that can make you

38:42.601 --> 38:44.041
be this shaken.

38:45.161 --> 38:46.402
One is Lin Tao,

38:47.762 --> 38:49.002
the other is Yu Yiming.

38:49.161 --> 38:49.721
Which one?

38:50.282 --> 38:51.721
Yu Yiming, of course.

38:54.962 --> 38:57.081
Young love during school days
was so simple.

38:57.721 --> 38:59.962
No need to think about
the future or the outcomes,

39:00.002 --> 39:01.561
just loved.

39:02.521 --> 39:03.561
But now,

39:03.762 --> 39:05.442
the more I want to be with someone,

39:06.121 --> 39:08.721
the more I can't help
thinking about reality.

39:13.121 --> 39:14.322
That means you've grown up.

39:15.842 --> 39:17.161
You used to be so carefree.

39:17.681 --> 39:19.376
How could you ever
ponder over such things?

39:19.641 --> 39:21.241
When I was young,

39:21.802 --> 39:23.561
I thought love was all sweet.

39:24.081 --> 39:25.521
But now I understand

39:26.322 --> 39:27.882
there isn't just sweetness,

39:27.882 --> 39:29.161
but bitterness,

39:29.521 --> 39:30.442
insecurity,

39:30.762 --> 39:31.402
pride,

39:31.601 --> 39:32.282
and pain.

39:32.842 --> 39:37.201
All kinds of contradictions intertwined.

39:38.002 --> 39:39.882
But I just can't let go.

39:50.521 --> 39:52.241
I understand how you feel right now.

39:58.081 --> 39:59.561
But this is what love is.

40:02.842 --> 40:05.081
Everything you just said

40:05.721 --> 40:07.521
is part of love.

40:09.442 --> 40:10.561
Don't run from it.

40:10.922 --> 40:12.041
You can't run anyway.

40:13.561 --> 40:15.802
So you could try to accept it,

40:16.442 --> 40:17.161
understand it,

40:17.922 --> 40:18.762
and feel it.

40:19.561 --> 40:21.482
Maybe in that process,

40:22.121 --> 40:23.681
you'll find the answers you seek.

40:24.962 --> 40:26.802
No need to drain yourself like this.

40:28.241 --> 40:29.241
That's true.

40:33.081 --> 40:33.922
I'll think about it.

40:34.121 --> 40:34.681
I'm leaving.

40:37.282 --> 40:37.842
Wait.

40:38.641 --> 40:39.601
Well...

40:40.081 --> 40:42.121
Don't forget the makeup class.

40:44.681 --> 40:45.201
Okay.

40:45.362 --> 40:45.882
Bye.

40:47.002 --> 40:47.842
Goodbye.

40:57.498 --> 41:01.360
(Yan Studio)

41:05.601 --> 41:06.282
Yu Yiming.

41:10.681 --> 41:11.760
You're here for my sister?

41:13.482 --> 41:13.962
Yes.

41:15.561 --> 41:16.561
Your coworkers said

41:16.802 --> 41:17.721
she isn't here.

41:18.601 --> 41:19.681
So I'm waiting here.

41:23.002 --> 41:24.362
Does she not want to see me?

41:26.362 --> 41:27.601
She really isn't here.

41:28.161 --> 41:30.442
This morning she had makeup class,

41:30.721 --> 41:32.362
this afternoon a beauty launch event.

41:32.802 --> 41:34.802
She's looking for the newest products

41:34.962 --> 41:36.521
and preparing for the entrance exams.

41:37.201 --> 41:38.041
She's busy.

41:38.322 --> 41:39.201
Even I barely see her.

41:39.762 --> 41:41.482
Don't overthink it.
She really isn't here.

41:43.721 --> 41:44.442
Got it.

41:45.322 --> 41:46.641
Qiao Lin has told me

41:46.641 --> 41:47.762
about you two.

41:49.121 --> 41:50.521
I think she's right.

41:52.041 --> 41:53.041
If you ignore

41:53.241 --> 41:55.041
these differences now,

41:55.442 --> 41:57.041
bigger issues might arise later.

41:57.882 --> 41:59.402
So you both should calm down

41:59.561 --> 42:00.601
and think carefully

42:00.962 --> 42:02.641
whether you can accept it.

42:04.681 --> 42:05.521
She's more rational

42:05.962 --> 42:07.081
than before.

42:07.802 --> 42:09.296
That means you're important to her.

42:09.922 --> 42:11.081
Do you get me?

42:13.081 --> 42:13.882
Okay, I understand.

42:15.882 --> 42:16.802
I'll wait patiently.

42:18.482 --> 42:19.521
These flowers...

42:19.641 --> 42:20.521
I'll give them to her.

42:21.721 --> 42:22.322
Thank you.

42:23.322 --> 42:23.922
I'm leaving.

42:25.322 --> 42:25.922
Take care.

42:40.561 --> 42:41.002
Hello?

42:42.922 --> 42:43.762
I'm Shen Haoming.

42:45.002 --> 42:45.922
Shen Haoming?

42:58.721 --> 42:59.521
What's up?

43:01.402 --> 43:01.922
Have a seat.

43:11.601 --> 43:12.161
Thank you.

43:13.922 --> 43:15.282
You like Xu Yan, don't you?

43:18.282 --> 43:19.482
Don't get me wrong.

43:20.041 --> 43:20.641
Yes.

43:21.882 --> 43:23.282
I had feelings for her,

43:24.402 --> 43:25.882
but that was many years ago.

43:26.442 --> 43:27.802
I admit when I saw her again,

43:28.402 --> 43:29.362
I still had a soft spot.

43:30.601 --> 43:32.041
But I know that's not love.

43:33.561 --> 43:35.241
Besides, I'm now with Qiao Lin.

43:39.161 --> 43:41.402
I know you're not involved with her.

43:42.322 --> 43:43.402
I asked you here today

43:44.362 --> 43:45.482
to request your help.

43:46.322 --> 43:47.201
How can I help?

43:47.762 --> 43:49.442
You've known her since childhood.

43:50.201 --> 43:51.721
You must understand her well, right?

43:53.201 --> 43:54.962
I hope you can help me win her back.

43:57.521 --> 43:58.521
You're mistaken.

43:59.002 --> 44:01.081
Qiao Lin and I have problems too.

44:02.922 --> 44:04.081
I don't know how to help you.

44:04.802 --> 44:06.041
Where are things now?

44:06.521 --> 44:07.632
Breakup cooling-off period.

44:10.282 --> 44:10.802
And you?

44:11.402 --> 44:12.560
Divorce cooling-off period.

44:12.721 --> 44:13.402
Let me toast you.

44:17.201 --> 44:18.362
So you're saying

44:19.561 --> 44:23.641
you used to think you didn't love her,
but now you've fallen for her again?

44:24.282 --> 44:24.962
No.

44:25.081 --> 44:26.762
After we broke up...

44:27.641 --> 44:28.802
It's not "fallen again".

44:30.201 --> 44:31.482
I've always loved her.

44:38.002 --> 44:40.282
But I've never felt this lost before.

44:40.962 --> 44:42.721
I don't know what to do

44:42.721 --> 44:44.282
to get her back.

44:44.842 --> 44:46.041
I only know one thing.

44:47.041 --> 44:48.081
I won't let her go.

44:48.362 --> 44:49.442
Let me tell you.

44:51.402 --> 44:52.362
I hadn't seen Xu Yan

44:52.402 --> 44:53.641
since high school graduation.

44:54.322 --> 44:56.081
When we met again in Jingzhou,

44:56.442 --> 44:57.721
she told me she was married.

44:58.121 --> 44:59.161
The way she said it

44:59.201 --> 45:00.482
was overflowing

45:00.802 --> 45:01.922
with happiness.

45:02.922 --> 45:03.962
The radiance

45:05.121 --> 45:06.161
on her face

45:07.561 --> 45:09.081
was something I'd never seen.

45:09.922 --> 45:10.641
Really?

45:11.041 --> 45:11.681
You got married?

45:15.241 --> 45:15.922
Yes, last month.

45:18.041 --> 45:18.962
Though it's a bit late,

45:20.201 --> 45:21.081
congratulations.

45:22.842 --> 45:24.762
I could tell she was truly happy then.

45:26.041 --> 45:26.882
It's all my fault.

45:27.402 --> 45:29.121
I've always been slow

45:29.121 --> 45:30.402
to express myself.

45:31.442 --> 45:32.681
Always realize things too late.

45:33.922 --> 45:34.922
You think you're alone?

45:38.521 --> 45:39.521
I'm the same.

45:40.002 --> 45:41.402
After I met Qiao Lin again,

45:42.322 --> 45:43.561
she's always by my side,

45:45.561 --> 45:46.402
supporting,

45:47.241 --> 45:48.081
encouraging,

45:49.842 --> 45:50.641
and caring.

45:54.442 --> 45:55.922
And it still takes me so long

45:57.201 --> 45:58.601
to realize that I like her.

46:05.802 --> 46:06.762
Let's team up.

46:07.641 --> 46:09.362
The women we love are sisters.

46:10.482 --> 46:11.442
Our love lives

46:12.721 --> 46:14.161
are just as bumpy.

46:15.201 --> 46:16.282
We need to help each other.

46:17.241 --> 46:17.762
Makes sense.

46:17.962 --> 46:18.882
When Lin ignores me,

46:19.442 --> 46:20.521
you can reach her for me.

46:20.842 --> 46:21.922
When Xu Yan avoids you,

46:22.521 --> 46:23.842
I can speak to her.

46:24.161 --> 46:24.882
That's...

46:26.561 --> 46:27.482
strength in numbers.

46:28.282 --> 46:29.962
Two are better than one.

46:30.322 --> 46:31.121
You're right.

46:31.802 --> 46:32.464
Brother-in-law.

46:32.882 --> 46:33.520
Brother-in-law.

46:35.442 --> 46:36.176
Brother-in-law.

46:36.402 --> 46:37.072
Brother-in-law.

46:40.410 --> 46:42.326
