ظآزTo reigniteظآز

48:18.864 --> 48:23.889
ظآزThe love I should deserveظآز

48:25.531 --> 48:28.537
ظآزWhen the time is rightظآز

48:28.537 --> 48:31.814
ظآزYou realizeظآز

48:31.814 --> 48:36.444
ظآزIt will all be alrightظآز

